<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">  
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Raleway:300i,400,500,700" rel="stylesheet"> 
    <link href="monapplication/view/css/materialize.min.css" type="text/css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="monapplication/view/css/style.css" type="text/css" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Bienvenue sur CINE CLUB</title>
</head>
<body class="amber lighten-4">
  <header>
    <nav class="amber lighten-4 h-80">
      <div class="nav-wrapper container valign-wrapper justify-content-between">
        <a class="valign-wrapper" href="#">
          <img class="responsive-img" src="monapplication/view/img/logo-film.png" alt="Logo">
        </a>
        <ul class="hide-on-med-and-down">
          <li>
            <a class="fs-20 grey-text text-darken-4" href="#">Ajouter un film</a>
          </li>
        </ul> 
        <ul id="nav-mobile" class="sidenav">
          <li>
            <a class="" href="#">Ajouter un film</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#" data-target="nav-mobile" class="sidenav-trigger"><i class="material-icons black-text">menu</i></a>
      </div>
      
    </nav>
  </header>
<!-- Section 1 Parallaxe/Main -->    
      <div id="index-banner" class="parallax-container">
        <div class="section no-pad-bot">
          <div class="container">
            <h1 class="center amber-text bold raleway fs-5">CINE CLUB</h1>
            <div class="row center">
              <h5 class="col s12 white-text raleway">Une bibliothèque de films étudiée par le DFCO</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="parallax">
          <img src="monapplication/view/img/salle.jpg" alt="Salle cinéma">
        </div>
      </div>
   
<!-- Section Random Films -->   
      <div class="container ptb-50">
        <div class="section">
          <div class="row">
            <h2 class="center grey-text text-darken-4 pb-60 separator">Films</h2>
            {% for film in randomFilms %}
              <div class="col s12 m4">
                <div class="card">
                  <div class="card-image">
                    <img class="h-500" src="{{ film.image_FILMS }}" alt="{{ film.titre_FILMS }}">     
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="card-title pl-24">{{ film.titre_FILMS }}</h3>
                  <div class="card-action">
                    <a class="blue-text text-darken-2" href="film/{{ film.id_FILMS }}">Descriptif du film</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            {% endfor %} 
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    
      <div class="parallax-container valign-wrapper">
        <div class="section no-pad-bot">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row center">
              <h5 class="header col s12 raleway italic bold amber-text fs-30">Proposer vos films bientôt sur la rubrique ''Ajouter un film''</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
          </div>
        <div class="parallax"><img src="monapplication/view/img/bobine.jpg" alt="Genre films"></div>
      </div>
    
      <div class="container ptb-50">
        <div class="section">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col s12 center">
              <h2 class="grey-text text-darken-4 pb-60 separator">Contact</h2>
              <p class="justify-align light fs-20">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam scelerisque id nunc nec volutpat. Etiam pellentesque tristique arcu, non consequat magna fermentum ac. Cras ut ultricies eros. Maecenas eros justo, ullamcorper a sapien id, viverra ultrices eros. Morbi sem neque, posuere et pretium eget, bibendum sollicitudin lacus. Aliquam eleifend sollicitudin diam, eu mattis nisl maximus sed. Nulla imperdiet semper molestie. Morbi massa odio, condimentum sed ipsum ac, gravida ultrices erat. Nullam eget dignissim mauris, non tristique erat. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia Curae;</p>
            </div>
          </div>
    
        </div>
      </div>
    
    
      <div class="parallax-container valign-wrapper">
        <div class="section no-pad-bot">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row center">
              <h5 class="header col s12 amber-text fs-30 raleway italic bold">Un descriptif complet sur chacune des affiches de film disponible.</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="parallax"><img src="monapplication/view/img/tournage.jpg" alt="Caméra cinéma"></div>
      </div>
    
      <footer class="page-footer amber lighten-4">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col l6 s12">
                <h5 class="amber-text raleway bold fs-20">Rechercher</h5>
                <nav class="amber lighten-5">
                  <div class="nav-wrapper">
                    <form>
                      <div class="input-field">
                        <input id="search" type="search" required>
                        <label class="label-icon" for="search"><i class="material-icons">search</i></label>
                        <i class="material-icons">close</i>
                      </div>
                    </form>
                  </div>
                </nav>
              </div>

            <div class="col offset-l2 l4  s12">
              <h5 class="amber-text raleway bold fs-20">A propos</h5>
              <p class="grey-text text-darken-4 roboto medium">
                Zombie ipsum reversus ab viral inferno, nam rick grimes malum cerebro.
                De carne lumbering animata corpora quaeritis.
                Summus brains sit​​.
              </p>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-copyright">
            <div class="container">
              <p class="left grey-text text-darken-4 roboto medium">© 2018 Copyright - 
                <span class="bold">CINE CLUB</span>
              </p>
              
              <div class="nav-wrapper right">
                
                <ul id="nav-mobile" class="d-flex hide-on-med-and-down">
                  <li class="ml-10"><a href="#" target="_blank">Erick B.</a></li>
                  <li class="ml-10"><a href="https://romainw.promo-18.codeur.online/" target="_blank">Romain W.</a></li>
                  <li class="ml-10"><a href="#" target="_blank">Jérome R.</a></li>
                  <li class="ml-10"><a href="#" target="_blank">Inès M.</a></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              
            </div>
          </div>
      </footer>

    <script src="monapplication/view/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="monapplication/view/js/materialize.min.js"></script>
    <script src="monapplication/view/js/init.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
